Source: English Language in Aust. & NZ, The
Author: TURNER
Vol / Page: 146
Edition:
Quote: There is the <i>Sunday dog</i> who declines to work in a difficulty, the <i>woolclasser</i> who bites at the sheep, and the sooner who would sooner rest than work.
